    <!-- Kleisli composition -->
    <h3>Kleisli composition</h3>
    <p>Morphisms in FinStoch compose via <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kleisli_category"><img src="/reading/wikipedia.svg" alt="wp" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>Kleisli composition</a>: feed the output distribution of f into g, marginalizing over the intermediate. This is <code>>>=</code> (bind) from monads.</p>

